  "name": "dutch-instruction-datasets",
  "description": "Data creation scripts to generate Dutch instruction datasets through OpenAI services, specifically using Azure services. This comprehensive toolkit provides multiple command-line tools for translating existing datasets to Dutch, generating responses using various models, building multi-turn conversations, adding language identification, and filtering out non-Dutch content with sophisticated rules. The package supports both Azure OpenAI and Hugging Face models with advanced features like quantization, parallel processing, and robust error handling.",
